      (objectness_logits): Conv2d(256, 3, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1))
      (anchor_deltas): Conv2d(256, 12, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1))
    )
    (anchor_generator): DefaultAnchorGenerator(
      (cell_anchors): BufferList()
    )
  )
  (roi_heads): StandardROIHeads(
    (box_pooler): ROIPooler(
      (level_poolers): ModuleList(
        (0): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.25, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
        (1): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.125, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
        (2): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.0625, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
        (3): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.03125, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
      )
    )
    (box_head): FastRCNNConvFCHead(
      (flatten): Flatten(start_dim=1, end_dim=-1)
      (fc1): Linear(in_features=12544, out_features=1024, bias=True)
      (fc_relu1): ReLU()
      (fc2): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=1024, bias=True)
      (fc_relu2): ReLU()
    )
    (box_predictor): FastRCNNOutputLayers(
      (cls_score): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=4, bias=True)
      (bbox_pred): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=12, bias=True)
    )
  )
)

  )

    (rpn_head): StandardRPNHead(
      (conv): Conv2d(256, 256, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1))

    )

      (cell_anchors): BufferList()
    )
  )
  (roi_heads): StandardROIHeads(

      (level_poolers): ModuleList(
        (0): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.25, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)

      )
    )

      (flatten): Flatten(start_dim=1, end_dim=-1)
      (fc1): Linear(in_features=12544, out_features=1024, bias=True)
      (fc_relu1): ReLU()
      (fc2): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=1024, bias=True)
      (fc_relu2): ReLU()
    )
    (box_predictor): FastRCNNOutputLayers(
      (cls_score): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=4, bias=True)
      (bbox_pred): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=12, bias=True)
    )
  )
)

            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv3): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
        )
        (18): BottleneckBlock(
          (conv1): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv2): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1), groups=32, bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv3): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
        )
        (19): BottleneckBlock(
          (conv1): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv2): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1), groups=32, bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv3): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
        )
        (20): BottleneckBlock(
          (conv1): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv2): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1), groups=32, bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv3): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
        )
        (21): BottleneckBlock(
          (conv1): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv2): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1), groups=32, bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv3): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
        )
        (22): BottleneckBlock(
          (conv1): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv2): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1), groups=32, bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv3): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
        )
      )
      (res5): Sequential(
        (0): BottleneckBlock(
          (shortcut): Conv2d(
            1024, 2048, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(2, 2), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv1): Conv2d(
            1024, 2048, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv2): Conv2d(
            2048, 2048, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(2, 2), padding=(1, 1), groups=32, bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv3): Conv2d(
            2048, 2048, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
        )
        (1): BottleneckBlock(
          (conv1): Conv2d(
            2048, 2048, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv2): Conv2d(
            2048, 2048, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1), groups=32, bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv3): Conv2d(
            2048, 2048, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
        )
        (2): BottleneckBlock(
          (conv1): Conv2d(
            2048, 2048, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv2): Conv2d(
            2048, 2048, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1), groups=32, bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv3): Conv2d(
            2048, 2048, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
        )
      )
    )
  )
  (proposal_generator): RPN(
    (rpn_head): StandardRPNHead(
      (conv): Conv2d(256, 256, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1))
      (objectness_logits): Conv2d(256, 3, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1))
      (anchor_deltas): Conv2d(256, 12, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1))
    )
    (anchor_generator): DefaultAnchorGenerator(
      (cell_anchors): BufferList()
    )
  )
  (roi_heads): StandardROIHeads(
    (box_pooler): ROIPooler(
      (level_poolers): ModuleList(
        (0): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.25, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
        (1): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.125, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
        (2): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.0625, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
        (3): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.03125, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
      )
    )
    (box_head): FastRCNNConvFCHead(
      (flatten): Flatten(start_dim=1, end_dim=-1)
      (fc1): Linear(in_features=12544, out_features=1024, bias=True)
      (fc_relu1): ReLU()
      (fc2): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=1024, bias=True)
      (fc_relu2): ReLU()
    )
    (box_predictor): FastRCNNOutputLayers(
      (cls_score): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=3, bias=True)
      (bbox_pred): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=8, bias=True)
    )
  )
)

    )
  )
  (proposal_generator): RPN(
    (rpn_head): StandardRPNHead(
      (conv): Conv2d(256, 256, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1))
      (objectness_logits): Conv2d(256, 3, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1))

      (cell_anchors): BufferList()
    )
  )
  (roi_heads): StandardROIHeads(
    (box_pooler): ROIPooler(
      (level_poolers): ModuleList(
        (0): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.25, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)

      )
    )

      (flatten): Flatten(start_dim=1, end_dim=-1)

      (fc_relu1): ReLU()

      (cls_score): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=3, bias=True)
      (bbox_pred): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=8, bias=True)
    )
  )

            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv2): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1), groups=32, bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv3): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
        )

          (conv1): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )

      )
      (res5): Sequential(
        (0): BottleneckBlock(
          (shortcut): Conv2d(

            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)

          )
          (conv3): Conv2d(

            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
        )

          (conv1): Conv2d(
            2048, 2048, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False

          )

          )
          (conv3): Conv2d(

          )

          (conv1): Conv2d(

          )
        )
      )
    )
  )
  (proposal_generator): RPN(
    (rpn_head): StandardRPNHead(
      (conv): Conv2d(256, 256, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1))
      (objectness_logits): Conv2d(256, 3, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1))
      (anchor_deltas): Conv2d(256, 12, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1))
    )
    (anchor_generator): DefaultAnchorGenerator(
      (cell_anchors): BufferList()
    )
  )
  (roi_heads): StandardROIHeads(
    (box_pooler): ROIPooler(
      (level_poolers): ModuleList(
        (0): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.25, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
        (1): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.125, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
        (2): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.0625, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
        (3): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.03125, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
      )
    )
    (box_head): FastRCNNConvFCHead(
      (flatten): Flatten(start_dim=1, end_dim=-1)
      (fc1): Linear(in_features=12544, out_features=1024, bias=True)
      (fc_relu1): ReLU()

      (fc_relu2): ReLU()
    )
    (box_predictor): FastRCNNOutputLayers(
      (cls_score): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=3, bias=True)
      (bbox_pred): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=8, bias=True)
    )
  )
)

        (0): BottleneckBlock(

          (conv3): Conv2d(

          )
        )

          (conv1): Conv2d(
            2048, 2048, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False

          )
          (conv2): Conv2d(
            2048, 2048, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1), groups=32, bias=False

          )
          (conv3): Conv2d(
            2048, 2048, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False

          )
        )
        (2): BottleneckBlock(
          (conv1): Conv2d(

            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )

          )
          (conv3): Conv2d(

            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
        )
      )
    )
  )
  (proposal_generator): RPN(
    (rpn_head): StandardRPNHead(
      (conv): Conv2d(256, 256, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1))
      (objectness_logits): Conv2d(256, 3, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1))
      (anchor_deltas): Conv2d(256, 12, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1))
    )
    (anchor_generator): DefaultAnchorGenerator(
      (cell_anchors): BufferList()
    )
  )
  (roi_heads): StandardROIHeads(
    (box_pooler): ROIPooler(
      (level_poolers): ModuleList(
        (0): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.25, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
        (1): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.125, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)

      )
    )

      (flatten): Flatten(start_dim=1, end_dim=-1)
      (fc1): Linear(in_features=12544, out_features=1024, bias=True)
      (fc_relu1): ReLU()
      (fc2): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=1024, bias=True)
      (fc_relu2): ReLU()

      (cls_score): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=2, bias=True)
      (bbox_pred): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=4, bias=True)
    )
  )
)

            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv2): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1), groups=32, bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv3): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
        )
      )
      (res5): Sequential(
        (0): BottleneckBlock(
          (shortcut): Conv2d(
            1024, 2048, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(2, 2), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv1): Conv2d(
            1024, 2048, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv2): Conv2d(
            2048, 2048, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(2, 2), padding=(1, 1), groups=32, bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv3): Conv2d(
            2048, 2048, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
        )
        (1): BottleneckBlock(
          (conv1): Conv2d(
            2048, 2048, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv2): Conv2d(
            2048, 2048, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1), groups=32, bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv3): Conv2d(
            2048, 2048, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
        )
        (2): BottleneckBlock(
          (conv1): Conv2d(
            2048, 2048, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv2): Conv2d(
            2048, 2048, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1), groups=32, bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv3): Conv2d(
            2048, 2048, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
        )
      )
    )
  )
  (proposal_generator): RPN(
    (rpn_head): StandardRPNHead(
      (conv): Conv2d(256, 256, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1))
      (objectness_logits): Conv2d(256, 3, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1))
      (anchor_deltas): Conv2d(256, 12, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1))
    )
    (anchor_generator): DefaultAnchorGenerator(
      (cell_anchors): BufferList()
    )
  )
  (roi_heads): StandardROIHeads(
    (box_pooler): ROIPooler(
      (level_poolers): ModuleList(
        (0): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.25, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
        (1): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.125, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
        (2): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.0625, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
        (3): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.03125, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
      )
    )
    (box_head): FastRCNNConvFCHead(
      (flatten): Flatten(start_dim=1, end_dim=-1)
      (fc1): Linear(in_features=12544, out_features=1024, bias=True)
      (fc_relu1): ReLU()
      (fc2): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=1024, bias=True)
      (fc_relu2): ReLU()
    )
    (box_predictor): FastRCNNOutputLayers(
      (cls_score): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=2, bias=True)
      (bbox_pred): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=4, bias=True)
    )
  )
)

            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )

          (conv1): Conv2d(

      )
    )
  )
  (proposal_generator): RPN(
    (rpn_head): StandardRPNHead(
      (conv): Conv2d(256, 256, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1))
      (objectness_logits): Conv2d(256, 3, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1))
      (anchor_deltas): Conv2d(256, 12, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1))
    )
    (anchor_generator): DefaultAnchorGenerator(
      (cell_anchors): BufferList()
    )
  )
  (roi_heads): StandardROIHeads(
    (box_pooler): ROIPooler(
      (level_poolers): ModuleList(
        (0): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.25, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
        (1): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.125, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
        (2): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.0625, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
        (3): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.03125, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
      )
    )
    (box_head): FastRCNNConvFCHead(
      (flatten): Flatten(start_dim=1, end_dim=-1)
      (fc1): Linear(in_features=12544, out_features=1024, bias=True)
      (fc_relu1): ReLU()
      (fc2): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=1024, bias=True)
      (fc_relu2): ReLU()
    )
    (box_predictor): FastRCNNOutputLayers(
      (cls_score): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=2, bias=True)
      (bbox_pred): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=4, bias=True)
    )
  )
)

        )
      )
    )
  )
  (proposal_generator): RPN(
    (rpn_head): StandardRPNHead(
      (conv): Conv2d(256, 256, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1))
      (objectness_logits): Conv2d(256, 3, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1))
      (anchor_deltas): Conv2d(256, 12, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1))
    )
    (anchor_generator): DefaultAnchorGenerator(
      (cell_anchors): BufferList()
    )
  )
  (roi_heads): StandardROIHeads(
    (box_pooler): ROIPooler(
      (level_poolers): ModuleList(
        (0): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.25, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
        (1): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.125, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
        (2): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.0625, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
        (3): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.03125, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
      )
    )
    (box_head): FastRCNNConvFCHead(
      (flatten): Flatten(start_dim=1, end_dim=-1)
      (fc1): Linear(in_features=12544, out_features=1024, bias=True)
      (fc_relu1): ReLU()
      (fc2): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=1024, bias=True)
      (fc_relu2): ReLU()
    )
    (box_predictor): FastRCNNOutputLayers(
      (cls_score): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=2, bias=True)
      (bbox_pred): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=4, bias=True)
    )
  )
)

            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )

          )

          )

            2048, 2048, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1), groups=32, bias=False

          )
          (conv3): Conv2d(

            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
        )

          (conv1): Conv2d(

            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )

            2048, 2048, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1), groups=32, bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv3): Conv2d(

            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
        )
      )
    )
  )
  (proposal_generator): RPN(
    (rpn_head): StandardRPNHead(
      (conv): Conv2d(256, 256, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1))
      (objectness_logits): Conv2d(256, 3, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1))
      (anchor_deltas): Conv2d(256, 12, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1))
    )
    (anchor_generator): DefaultAnchorGenerator(
      (cell_anchors): BufferList()
    )
  )
  (roi_heads): StandardROIHeads(
    (box_pooler): ROIPooler(
      (level_poolers): ModuleList(
        (0): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.25, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
        (1): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.125, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
        (2): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.0625, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
        (3): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.03125, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
      )
    )
    (box_head): FastRCNNConvFCHead(
      (flatten): Flatten(start_dim=1, end_dim=-1)
      (fc1): Linear(in_features=12544, out_features=1024, bias=True)
      (fc_relu1): ReLU()
      (fc2): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=1024, bias=True)
      (fc_relu2): ReLU()
    )
    (box_predictor): FastRCNNOutputLayers(
      (cls_score): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=2, bias=True)
      (bbox_pred): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=4, bias=True)
    )
  )
)

  (proposal_generator): RPN(
    (rpn_head): StandardRPNHead(
      (conv): Conv2d(256, 256, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1))
      (objectness_logits): Conv2d(256, 3, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1))
      (anchor_deltas): Conv2d(256, 12, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1))
    )
    (anchor_generator): DefaultAnchorGenerator(
      (cell_anchors): BufferList()
    )
  )
  (roi_heads): StandardROIHeads(
    (box_pooler): ROIPooler(
      (level_poolers): ModuleList(
        (0): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.25, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
        (1): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.125, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
        (2): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.0625, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
        (3): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.03125, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
      )
    )
    (box_head): FastRCNNConvFCHead(
      (flatten): Flatten(start_dim=1, end_dim=-1)
      (fc1): Linear(in_features=12544, out_features=1024, bias=True)
      (fc_relu1): ReLU()
      (fc2): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=1024, bias=True)
      (fc_relu2): ReLU()
    )
    (box_predictor): FastRCNNOutputLayers(
      (cls_score): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=2, bias=True)
      (bbox_pred): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=4, bias=True)
    )
  )
)

          (conv2): Conv2d(

        (0): BottleneckBlock(

          )
          (conv3): Conv2d(

          )
          (conv3): Conv2d(

          )

      )
    )
  )
  (proposal_generator): RPN(
    (rpn_head): StandardRPNHead(
      (conv): Conv2d(256, 256, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1))
      (objectness_logits): Conv2d(256, 3, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1))
      (anchor_deltas): Conv2d(256, 12, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1))
    )
    (anchor_generator): DefaultAnchorGenerator(
      (cell_anchors): BufferList()
    )
  )
  (roi_heads): StandardROIHeads(
    (box_pooler): ROIPooler(
      (level_poolers): ModuleList(
        (0): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.25, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
        (1): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.125, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)

      )
    )

      (fc1): Linear(in_features=12544, out_features=1024, bias=True)
      (fc_relu1): ReLU()

      (fc_relu2): ReLU()

    (box_predictor): FastRCNNOutputLayers(
      (cls_score): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=2, bias=True)
      (bbox_pred): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=4, bias=True)
    )
  )
)

          )
        )
        (18): BottleneckBlock(
          (conv1): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv2): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1), groups=32, bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv3): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
        )
        (19): BottleneckBlock(
          (conv1): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv2): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1), groups=32, bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv3): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
        )
        (20): BottleneckBlock(
          (conv1): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv2): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1), groups=32, bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv3): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
        )
        (21): BottleneckBlock(
          (conv1): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv2): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1), groups=32, bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv3): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
        )
        (22): BottleneckBlock(
          (conv1): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv2): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1), groups=32, bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv3): Conv2d(
            1024, 1024, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=1024, eps=1e-05)
          )
        )
      )
      (res5): Sequential(
        (0): BottleneckBlock(
          (shortcut): Conv2d(
            1024, 2048, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(2, 2), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv1): Conv2d(
            1024, 2048, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv2): Conv2d(
            2048, 2048, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(2, 2), padding=(1, 1), groups=32, bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv3): Conv2d(
            2048, 2048, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
        )
        (1): BottleneckBlock(
          (conv1): Conv2d(
            2048, 2048, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv2): Conv2d(
            2048, 2048, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1), groups=32, bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv3): Conv2d(
            2048, 2048, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
        )
        (2): BottleneckBlock(
          (conv1): Conv2d(
            2048, 2048, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv2): Conv2d(
            2048, 2048, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1), groups=32, bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
          (conv3): Conv2d(
            2048, 2048, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False
            (norm): FrozenBatchNorm2d(num_features=2048, eps=1e-05)
          )
        )
      )
    )
  )
  (proposal_generator): RPN(
    (rpn_head): StandardRPNHead(
      (conv): Conv2d(256, 256, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1))
      (objectness_logits): Conv2d(256, 3, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1))
      (anchor_deltas): Conv2d(256, 12, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1))
    )
    (anchor_generator): DefaultAnchorGenerator(
      (cell_anchors): BufferList()
    )
  )
  (roi_heads): StandardROIHeads(
    (box_pooler): ROIPooler(
      (level_poolers): ModuleList(
        (0): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.25, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
        (1): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.125, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
        (2): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.0625, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
        (3): ROIAlign(output_size=(7, 7), spatial_scale=0.03125, sampling_ratio=0, aligned=True)
      )
    )
    (box_head): FastRCNNConvFCHead(
      (flatten): Flatten(start_dim=1, end_dim=-1)
      (fc1): Linear(in_features=12544, out_features=1024, bias=True)
      (fc_relu1): ReLU()
      (fc2): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=1024, bias=True)
      (fc_relu2): ReLU()
    )
    (box_predictor): FastRCNNOutputLayers(
      (cls_score): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=2, bias=True)
      (bbox_pred): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=4, bias=True)
    )
  )
)
